106	1817	4	24.3.4 Caulking Techniques .
107	1821	18	Removal of old caulking from leaking seams and recaulking is the standard method for repairing deck leaks .
108	1839	20	Fill the caulked seams with a black polyurethane seam filler , per the requirements of reference ( c ) .
109	1859	10	Before filling , caulk the seams with sufficient cotton .
110	1869	14	Seam out gaging ( beveling ) as specified in reference ( d ) .
